item.title: a cover of Budapest !!
item.description:
hii guys!! I had footage still from my most recent trip and figured this song was perfect for it. ALSO, I just announced a small European tour next November supporting Bertie Newman, and couldn't be more excited to perform for the first time in Europe :) tickets are available with the link below and you can follow my Instagram for more updates! I guess that's it for now, take care and hope you enjoy xx https://linktr.ee/mariannebeaulieu
#cover #cinematic #budapest #travel #acoustic
